				<td colspan="2"><span>Eldrig just takes paitence.  Check in the zone for eldrig often to see if he is up.  There is usually someone there to help take him down.  If you are 56 you can do the high sun trick.  If he still doesnt spawn for you, go do something fun and come back again another day.
<br />

<br />
Phinni is easy but a pain.  He is on a regular timer and often there is a group of people who gather at his spawn time to kill him.  Just ask to join and log in every 12 hours until you get your backbone.  It took me 5 days or so.
<br />

<br />
Fear is hard because people dont like to go there.  Most folks have bad memories of long CRs.  There are other epics that require fear so try to find a Beserker or Necro that needs a fear raid and tag along.
<br />

<br />
Depending upon your server you will probably have to buy the white scale as Gore is likely perma killed.  The red scale is easier as many mobs can drop it including Ragefire for the cleric epic.
<br />

<br />
Good luck.
<br />

<br />
Tin.</span></td>
